  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3145269/" class="title-link">转：“不裁”之美，“毛边”之味</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3145269"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/tonytonyfeng/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4625645-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/tonytonyfeng/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">judetheobscure</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-04-07"
      class="main-meta">2010-04-07 12:07:06</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3145269_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  “不裁”之美 “毛边”之味 ——上海译文出版社推出“毛边本”系列经典随笔  毛边本是指图书在印刷装订时，最后一道纸边不予切割，读者在阅读时需要逐页自己裁开。毛边书最早出现在古代欧洲，法国、德国、英国等一些经济发达的欧洲国家的出版商曾为中古的贵族阶层生产过毛边书...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3145269/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">9有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3145269_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3145269_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





